description: 144 tissue samples from postmortem lung, liver, kidney, heart, spleen, testis and thyroid collected from 19 COVID-19 cases and 74 control specimens from 56 non-COVID-19 individuals were analyzed by PCT and TMT 16-plex based proteomics.

modifications.name: No PTMs are included in the dataset
